      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Start Ok                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to      prn-str-ini-999.
       prn-str-ini-900.
